Package io.artframework

Interface ResolverFactory<TType>

  • Type Parameters:
    TType - the type that is resolved by the resolver
    All Superinterfaces:
    Scoped
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    DefaultResolverFactory
    public interface ResolverFactory<TType>
extends Scoped
    The ResolverFactory is responsible for creating new instances of the given resolver type.

    One factory for each resolver is created automatically when registered with the ResolverProvider.
